This is an open source, you could change it whatever you want.
This is an unfinished code , so I will keep updating it.
The set_up way is same as spider_code_hc, so you can check that Readme.
For different size of your robot you need to change the variables in config.py
There is a picture to show how I calculate the inverse_kinematic.
To run this code :
1.You have to open running.py
2.Change the different movement_mode into loop function.
3.Run it.